OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FCampaigners have handed over a 2,500-
OL,7,Fsignature petition at Annan Town Hall
OL,8,Fcalling for Dumfries and Galloway
OL,9,FCouncil to re-adopt two local
OL,10,Ffootbridges, to replace the pair that
OL,11,Fwere washed away by flood water in
OL,12,FOctober 2021.
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway Council
OL,15,Fmaintained and inspected the previous
OL,16,Fbridges, called the Cuthberson
OL,17,FMemorial Bridge and the Diamond
OL,18,FJubilee Bridge, but says it is not
OL,19,Fplanning to do the same with the
OL,20,Fbridges that a local community group
OL,21,Fwants to fundraise to rebuild.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FCampaigner Fiona Robson told ITV
OL,7,FBorder, "The bridges had been there
OL,8,Ffor a long, long, time and we walked
OL,9,Fover those bridges with our
OL,10,Fgrandparents, we've walked over them
OL,11,Fwith our children, and we hoped that
OL,12,Fwe would walk over them with our
OL,13,Fgrandchildren. We can't if the council
OL,14,Fdon't support us."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FThe Diamond Jubilee Bridge was built
OL,7,Fin 1897 to commemorate Queen
OL,8,FVictoria's 60th year on the throne,
OL,9,Fand the Cuthbertson Memorial Bridge
OL,10,Fwas created in 1957 in memory of the
OL,11,Fmen and women of Annan who gave their
OL,12,Flives in the Second World War.
OL,14,FAnnan Tale of Two Bridges says in an
OL,15,Fideal world they would rebuild both
OL,16,Fbridges, but it may just be one. The
OL,17,Fcost of rebuilding each bridge would
OL,18,Fbe in the region of #1.5m-#2million.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FThe group says any funder would be
OL,7,Flooking for the bridge to be
OL,8,Fmaintained after it is built, so they
OL,9,Ffear they may not get funding without
OL,10,Fthat agreement from the council in
OL,11,Fplace. Fiona Robson adds, "People are
OL,12,Fshocked, people feel like the council
OL,13,Fshould be building them, and so given
OL,14,Fthat we're offering them a free bridge
OL,15,Fthat we will fund ourselves and they
OL,16,Fwon't accept that is a real shock to
OL,17,Fthe people of Annan."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FThe group argues the council has the
OL,7,Fstaff to inspect the bridges, and the
OL,8,Fbridges would be in much better
OL,9,Fcondition than the older bridges they
OL,10,Fare replacing.
OL,12,FDumfries and Galloway Council had said
OL,13,Fin March that "the former bridges were
OL,14,Fnot council assets, were not situated
OL,15,Fon council land and did not carry
OL,16,Fadopted public roads or adopted
OL,17,Ffootpaths", which is why "the project
OL,18,Fis not a council-led capital project".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FIt said it had supported the community
OL,7,Fgroup to progress a feasibility study,
OL,8,Fbut saw its role "in an advisory
OL,9,Fcapacity" only.
OL,11,FThe authority added: "We recognise the
OL,12,Faspirations of the Annan community to
OL,13,Fsee any path over a replacement bridge
OL,14,Fforming part of the council's core
OL,15,Fpaths plan. A process to review the
OL,16,Fcore path plan is currently being
OL,17,Fmobilised and this and any future
OL,18,Freviews are highly consultative with
OL,19,Fpaths identified by communities a
OL,20,Fpriority.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,F"Although the inclusion of a path over
OL,7,Fa new bridge as a core path could be
OL,8,Fachieved, under the legislative
OL,9,Fframework of the Land Reform
OL,10,F(Scotland) Act 2003, it does not
OL,11,Ffollow that the council is required to
OL,12,Fundertake maintenance or accept
OL,13,Fliability for any structures over
OL,14,Fwhich a core path may be designated.
OL,16,F"The council is committed to working
OL,17,Fwith the ATOTB group and will be
OL,18,Fmeeting with them soon to develop a
OL,19,Fletter of support to enable the group
OL,20,Fto continue with confidence."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778771469
OL,3,CPetition calls for council to re-adopt
OL,4,CAnnan footbridges
OL,6,FCampaigner Fiona Robson disagrees. She
OL,7,Fsaid: "They're also a route to the
OL,8,Fcemetery, a route to the rugby ground,
OL,9,Fthey're also a circular walk - during
OL,10,Fcovid times they got most of the
OL,11,Fcommunity out and about and walking in
OL,12,Fthe fresh air and a lot of us wouldn't
OL,13,Fhave got through it without them.
OL,15,F"We're the third-largest town in the
OL,16,Fregion and we're not getting what we
OL,17,Fdeserve."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
